ate of the kinematic dynamos.Finally we notice the footprint of\nthe inner-core in the magnetic field generated deep in the bulk of the shell,\nalthough we did not include one in our computations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Jun 2015 09:04:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Sep 2015 11:43:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 5 Nov 2015 10:42:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-20"}
